page.title: 10Square 9
page.content: This square is mainly covered by{ {Cultivated Grass.}It is highly managed by the farmers. There is also a small {Deciduous woodland}in this square. There are very few houses in this square, and those which are, are for workers on the{Westminster Estate. { }The land in this square is all privately owned by the estate, and all Housing is rented accomodation. { { Attitudes { }All the residents of this square were happy with the quiet lives which they live. They said that occasionly it is necessary to visit the major city, which is several miles away, but this is alright because travel is simple via good roads and a good bus service.
